original: Johansson, Gösta Sven August, tandläkare, Falköping, f. 2/4/09 i Sä-tuna, Skarab. 1., av Gustaf Adolf J. o. Emma Carlsson. G. 35 m. Irene Härdner. Barn: Ulf f. 36, Per 37, Birgitta 39. — Stud:ex. i Skara 30, med. stud. i Upps. 31-32, tandhkand. 33, tandl. 35. Prakt, i Falköp. sed. 35.
translated: Johansson, Gösta Sven August, dentist, Falköping, b. 2/4/09 in Sätuna, Skaraborg County, son of Gustaf Adolf J. and Emma Carlsson. Married in 1935 to Irene Härdner and they have three children: Ulf b. 1936, Per b. 1937, Birgitta b. 1939. He graduated from Skara High School in 1930, studied medicine at Uppsala University from 1931-1932, graduated from dental school in 1933, and became a licensed dentist in 1935. He has been practicing dentistry in Falköping since then.
